comments: Leonard (LAC) briefly grasps Murray's (DEN) arm off-ball and marginal contact occurs as Leonard (LAC) releases away to retrieve the post entry pass.
Murray (DEN) is moving alongside Leonard's (LAC) path and marginal body contact occurs during Leonard's drive.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Leonard's (LAC) arm.
Gordon (LAC) places his hand to Murray's (DEN) side defending over the screen and removes his arm defending his drive without applying force.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Gordon's (LAC) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Jokic (DEN) brings his hands toward Gordon's (LAC) side and marginal contact occurs as Jokic (DEN) releases away to roll.
Leonard (LAC) extends his arm into Jokic's (DEN) path and slides his arm against Jokic's front during his shot attempt near the rim.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) briefly places his hand against Leonard's (LAC) lower body off ball and immediately slides his hand off as they disengage.
Leonard (LAC) slightly extends his arm against Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) backside as he deflects the entry pass.
Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Leonard (LAC) establishes himself in Brown's (DEN) path with his arms slightly out of frame of his body and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Brown (DEN) contests George's (LAC) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Jokic (DEN) brushes Leonard's (LAC) arm and marginal contact occurs at the start of his drive.
Brown (DEN) and Leonard (LAC) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Replay review of the foul called on Caldwell-Pope (DEN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Caldwell-Pope (DEN) swipes down and pulls Plumlee's (LAC) hand off the ball.
Leonard (LAC) and Jokic (DEN) come together off ball and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs.
Leonard (LAC) briefly grasps Jokic's (DEN) arm during the pick and immediately slides his hand off as he hedges the pick.
Leonard (LAC) makes clean contact with the ball and cleanly dislodges it away from Murray (DEN) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Leonard (LAC) makes contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Murray (DEN) prior to incidental body contact occurring.
Jokic (DEN) briefly places his arm against George's (LAC) body and marginal body contact occurs as they pursue the loose ball.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) and George (LAC) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Gordon (LAC) establishes himself in Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Leonard (LAC) establishes himself in Brown's (DEN) path and does not deliver contact.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) moves laterally into George's (LAC) path and initiates lower body contact that affects George's SQBR during the drive.
Brown (DEN) establishes himself in George's (LAC) path and slightly extends his arms as they disengage.
After communicating with the Replay Center, George's (LAC) shot attempt was confirmed to be a no basket.
